Syntax: whittle <object> <wood>

  The whittle skill allows you to make various objects from special
wood objects.  Whittling requires a great deal of time and you must
be wielding a slash or pierce weapon to perform it.  Whittling is
not a skill for the faint of heart as resulting injuries can prove
to be severe.

There are many objects that can be made like:
  small toy boats
  small boxes
With a little training one could also make:
  training swords
  training staffs
Rangers with good training can also whittle various arrows and
bows for use in their training.

There are many objects that can be made with the whittle skill,
discovery is one of the joys of being a whittler.

